# PBP Stats (WNBA Totals → Player) — Master Schema (Table Data → Column Groupings)

This file merges the category→metric mappings captured from the PBP Stats **Totals → Player** table views (WNBA).  
Use it as a canonical taxonomy to **auto-tag columns** in BigQuery / Sheets / Notion.

---

## Universal ID / Context Fields (appear across most tables)
- Name
- Team
- GP (Games Played)
- Minutes

---

## Assists
**Core**
- Assists
- Assist Pts

**By shot type**
- 2pt
- 3pt

**By shot location**
- At Rim (≤ 4ft)
- SMR (Short Mid-Range; 4–14ft)
- LMR (Long Mid-Range; ≥14ft 2PT)
- C3 (Corner 3)
- AB3 (Arc / Above-the-Break 3)

---

## Rebounds
**Aggregate**
- Reb
- DReb
- OReb

**Defensive Rebounding — by shot type**
- FT DReb
- FT DReb%
- 2Pt DReb
- 2Pt DReb%
- 3Pt DReb
- 3Pt DReb%
- FG DReb%

**Offensive Rebounding — by shot type**
- FT OReb
- FT OReb%
- 2Pt OReb
- 2Pt OReb%
- 3Pt OReb
- 3Pt OReb%
- FG OReb%

**By location**
- Rim DReb%
- SMR DReb%
- LMR DReb%
- AB3 DReb%
- C3 DReb%
- Rim OReb%
- SMR OReb%
- LMR OReb%
- AB3 OReb%
- C3 OReb%

**Self-rebounding (putbacks)**
- Z-Bounds
- Z-Bound Pct

---

