## Shot Distribution
**Global**
- Shot Quality
- Rim or 3 Freq
- Avg 2pt Shot Distance
- Avg 3pt Shot Distance

**At Rim (≤4ft)**
- Rim FGM
- Rim FGA
- Rim Freq
- Rim FG%
- Unblocked Rim FG%
- Rim %AST
- % of Rim FGAB

**Short Mid-Range (SMR ~4–14ft)**
- SMR FGM
- SMR FGA
- SMR Freq
- SMR FG%
- Unblocked SMR FG%
- SMR %AST
- % of SMR FGAB

**Long Mid-Range (LMR ≥14ft, 2PT)**
- LMR FGM
- LMR FGA
- LMR Freq
- LMR FG%
- Unblocked LMR FG%
- LMR %AST
- % of LMR FGAB

**Corner 3 (C3)**
- C3 FGM
- C3 FGA
- C3 Freq
- C3 FG%
- Unblocked C3 FG%
- C3 %AST
- % of C3 FGAB

**Above-the-Break 3 (AB3)**
- AB3 FGM
- AB3 FGA
- AB3 Freq
- AB3 FG%
- Unblocked AB3 FG%
- AB3 %AST
- % of AB3 FGAB

**Non-Heave 3s**
- Non-Heave AB3 FGM
